snippet: The soprano Jennifer Zetlan performed on Thursday at Alice Tully Hall in a recital that was her prize for winning the Alice Tully Vocal Arts Award.
abstract: Corinna da Fonseca-Wollheim reviews performance by soprano Jennifer Zetlan at Alice Tully Hall.
